ly developed a new SPH scheme\nfor the simulations of vortex lattice formation in rotating BECs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2023 20:28:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 12 Mar 2023 15:51:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-19"}
