d, applied to stanene, confirm the absence of an excitonic\ninsulator phase, thus validating our results obtained by ab initio modeling of\n$\\alpha_{2{\\rm D}}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2023 14:26:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 14:55:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-28"}
